title: Home
text:
This project serves as a continuation of my midterm project, which investigates geotemporal mortality patterns in the United States before (2014-2019) and during COVID-19 (2020-2023) pandemic.
Here, I extend the analysis to worldwide using the mortality data from the WHO to evaluate global geotemporal mortality patterns. Detailed data processing pipeline can be found here.

title: Data Processing
text: Here, parts 4-6 of ICD-10 mortality data (corresponding to 2013 onward), as well as corresponding country codes, country-years availability, reference population and live births, were downloaded from WHO.
